title: MisterMusic Show 357 - new indie, altenative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 357 [192 kbps mp3] 2 hours.


On the show this week, new tunes from Stereophonics, The Mary Onettes, Cheers Elephant, and The Helio Sequence.
We travel back 25 years to June 1990, for the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was number 1 on the modern rock chart for 5 weeks that summer.
It's a blend of indie and alternative music mixed with over 5 decades of hits. Broadcasting weekly, and heard globally, It's the MisterMusic Show.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
